{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":100,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_huo_ji","speaker_name":"伙计","listener":null,"text":"是的，他包下了最好的一个院子，有花园，花厅，还有十几个大房间。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":84,"line_end":86},{"speaker":"char_wen_hua_de_ren","speaker_name":"问话的人","listener":"char_huo_ji","text":"他只住一人吧？","tone":"疑问","chapter":18,"line_start":88,"line_end":88},{"speaker":"char_huo_ji","speaker_name":"伙计","listener":null,"text":"不！两个人，还有一个赶车子的，像尊金刚。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":90,"line_end":90},{"speaker":"char_wen_hua_de_ren","speaker_name":"问话的人","listener":"char_huo_ji","text":"两个人为何包一个院子？","tone":"疑问","chapter":18,"line_start":92,"line_end":92},{"speaker":"char_huo_ji","speaker_name":"伙计","listener":null,"text":"不知道，或许是要请客吧。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":94,"line_end":94},{"speaker":"char_wen_hua_de_ren","speaker_name":"问话的人","listener":"char_huo_ji","text":"请客？他要请谁？","tone":"疑问","chapter":18,"line_start":96,"line_end":96},{"speaker":"char_huo_ji","speaker_name":"伙计","listener":null,"text":"不知道，但客人很多，而且好像是很重要的客人，因为他要我们向城里最好的酒楼里去订下十桌最好的酒席，然后又要我们把城里最漂亮的妓女都叫了去，至少要叫五十个。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":98,"line_end":100}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_ding_peng","name":"丁鹏","alias":[],"identity":"江湖新崛起的刀客，圆月弯刀传人","faction":null,"role":"protagonist","archetype":"warrior","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"圆月弯刀传人，与谢晓峰齐名的年轻刀客","personality":{"traits":["果敢决断","风流倜傥","重情重义","豪迈不羁","深谋远虑"],"speech_style":"直率大胆，偶尔带有调侃意味","temperament":"豪迈洒脱"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":["skill_yuan_yue_wan_dao"],"related_skills":["skill_yuan_yue_wan_dao"],"rag_refs":[18],"source_refs":[{"chapter":18,"line_start":4,"line_end":4,"text":"丁鹏离开了神剑山庄后"}]},{"id":"char_a_gu","name":"阿古","alias":[],"identity":"丁鹏的忠仆，聋哑人","faction":null,"role":"companion","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"丁鹏的忠仆，聋哑兼备，鞭法精绝","personality":{"traits":["忠诚不二","沉默寡言","武艺高强","心思细腻","勇猛无畏"],"speech_style":"不说话，用手势和动作表达","temperament":"沉稳忠厚"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_ding_peng","type":"主仆","intensity":90,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"忠心耿耿"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[18],"source_refs":[{"chapter":18,"line_start":2,"line_end":2,"text":"阿古的长鞭在空中飞舞着"}]},{"id":"char_huo_ji","name":"伙计","alias":[],"identity":"旅馆伙计","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":"scholar","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"旅馆伙计，贪财爱小便宜","personality":{"traits":["贪财好利","能说会道","机灵圆滑","爱占便宜","见钱眼开"],"speech_style":"市井气息，善于奉承","temperament":"圆滑世故"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[18],"source_refs":[{"chapter":18,"line_start":80,"line_end":80,"text":"一个伙计就被抓住了"}]},{"id":"char_wen_hua_de_ren","name":"问话的人","alias":[],"identity":"江湖人","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":"scholar","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"询问丁鹏下落的江湖人","personality":{"traits":["好奇","爱凑热闹","善于打听","胆小谨慎","爱八卦"],"speech_style":"市井气息，善于打听消息","temperament":"好奇八卦"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[18],"source_refs":[{"chapter":18,"line_start":80,"line_end":80,"text":"那些江湖人虽然不敢去问丁鹏"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":2,"line_start":101,"line_end":200,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_wen_hua_de_ren","speaker_name":"问话的人","listener":"char_huo_ji","text":"城里最漂亮的妓女有多少？","tone":"疑问","chapter":18,"line_start":102,"line_end":102},{"speaker":"char_huo_ji","speaker_name":"伙计","listener":null,"text":"天地良心，连最丑的加上去，也不到五十个，可是那位公子出手太豪华了，每一个妓女赏银是十两金子，因此没有也得给他找去。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":104,"line_end":106},{"speaker":"char_wen_hua_de_ren","speaker_name":"问话的人","listener":"char_huo_ji","text":"找得到吗？","tone":"疑问","chapter":18,"line_start":108,"line_end":108},{"speaker":"char_huo_ji","speaker_name":"伙计","listener":null,"text":"有十两金子，即使不是妓女也肯卖一次了，我有两个妹妹，加上我老婆，就可以抵三个了。","tone":"得意","chapter":18,"line_start":110,"line_end":112},{"speaker":"char_wen_hua_de_ren","speaker_name":"问话的人","listener":"char_huo_ji","text":"什么？你要把自己的老婆跟妹妹叫去当妓女？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":18,"line_start":114,"line_end":114},{"speaker":"char_huo_ji","speaker_name":"伙计","listener":null,"text":"是的，一次能赚十两金子的机会实在不多，只可惜我的女儿太小，只有五岁，否则我还可以多赚十两。","tone":"得意","chapter":18,"line_start":116,"line_end":118},{"speaker":"char_wen_hua_de_ren","speaker_name":"问话的人","listener":"char_huo_ji","text":"那你就快去吧，别耽误了你发财的机会。","tone":"无奈","chapter":18,"line_start":120,"line_end":122},{"speaker":"char_du_ling_ling","speaker_name":"杜玲玲","listener":"char_huo_ji","text":"喂！你一时找不到那么多，就把我们姊妹俩也凑上如何？","tone":"调侃","chapter":18,"line_start":138,"line_end":140},{"speaker":"char_du_zhen_zhen","speaker_name":"杜珍珍","listener":"char_huo_ji","text":"我们不要金子，那全部归你，而且还贴你二十两银子。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":144,"line_end":146},{"speaker":"char_huo_ji","speaker_name":"伙计","listener":null,"text":"二位姑娘，你们还有没有同伴，也要干同样买卖的？","tone":"好奇","chapter":18,"line_start":150,"line_end":152},{"speaker":"char_du_ling_ling","speaker_name":"杜玲玲","listener":"char_huo_ji","text":"你倒是不知足呀，像这种好生意做一回还不过瘾？","tone":"调侃","chapter":18,"line_start":154,"line_end":156},{"speaker":"char_huo_ji","speaker_name":"伙计","listener":null,"text":"上个月我算了个命，看相的王瞎子说我今年会走偏财运，会发一百两金子的横财，我起初以为他胡说，哪知道今天财神爷果然来照顾了，我家里有三个人，加上二位姑娘就是五十两了，王瞎子的相既然如此灵验，我想一定还有五十两的。","tone":"得意","chapter":18,"line_start":158,"line_end":160},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"","listener":null,"text":"不错，那个瞎子看相的确很准，你应该好好地请他再帮你看一看。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":162,"line_end":164}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_du_ling_ling","name":"杜玲玲","alias":["黑水仙"],"identity":"江湖女剑客，镖师","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"略有小成","one_line":"杜家姊妹的姐姐，外号黑水仙","personality":{"traits":["胆大心细","爱凑热闹","机灵古怪","爱慕虚荣","果断决绝"],"speech_style":"市井气息，善于调侃","temperament":"活泼开朗"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_du_zhen_zhen","type":"亲属","intensity":80,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"姐妹情深"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[18],"source_refs":[{"chapter":18,"line_start":128,"line_end":128,"text":"姊姊叫杜玲玲"}]},{"id":"char_du_zhen_zhen","name":"杜珍珍","alias":["白水仙"],"identity":"江湖女剑客，镖师","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"略有小成","one_line":"杜家姊妹的妹妹，外号白水仙","personality":{"traits":["胆大心细","爱凑热闹","机灵古怪","爱慕虚荣","果断决绝"],"speech_style":"市井气息，善于调侃","temperament":"活泼开朗"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_du_ling_ling","type":"亲属","intensity":80,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"姐妹情深"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[18],"source_refs":[{"chapter":18,"line_start":128,"line_end":128,"text":"妹妹叫杜珍珍"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":3,"line_start":201,"line_end":300,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_ding_peng","speaker_name":"丁鹏","listener":null,"text":"你们不都是吗？","tone":"微笑","chapter":18,"line_start":210,"line_end":210},{"speaker":"char_mei_mei","speaker_name":"美美","listener":null,"text":"公子的客人就是我们？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":18,"line_start":212,"line_end":212},{"speaker":"char_xian_xian","speaker_name":"仙仙","listener":null,"text":"公子，为什么呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":18,"line_start":224,"line_end":224},{"speaker":"char_ding_peng","speaker_name":"丁鹏","listener":null,"text":"难道以前没有别的客人下条子叫你们过？","tone":"微笑","chapter":18,"line_start":226,"line_end":226},{"speaker":"char_xian_xian","speaker_name":"仙仙","listener":null,"text":"那当然有。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":228,"line_end":228},{"speaker":"char_ding_peng","speaker_name":"丁鹏","listener":null,"text":"别人叫你们来为了什么呢？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":230,"line_end":230},{"speaker":"char_mei_mei","speaker_name":"美美","listener":null,"text":"是为了要我们侍候。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":232,"line_end":232},{"speaker":"char_ding_peng","speaker_name":"丁鹏","listener":null,"text":"我也是为了这个原因。","tone":"微笑","chapter":18,"line_start":234,"line_end":234},{"speaker":"char_xian_xian","speaker_name":"仙仙","listener":null,"text":"公子，不是这样子侍候的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":236,"line_end":236},{"speaker":"char_ding_peng","speaker_name":"丁鹏","listener":null,"text":"我知道，我也不是第一次出条子叫堂差，男人们到这儿来，无非是为了酒色，先喝喝酒，增加点情趣，等情投意合的时候，再一起上床……","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":238,"line_end":238},{"speaker":"char_xian_xian","speaker_name":"仙仙","listener":null,"text":"公子总不会要我们五十个人都侍候您上床吧？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":242,"line_end":242},{"speaker":"char_qing_qing","speaker_name":"青青","listener":null,"text":"你这个方法实在很特别。","tone":"微笑","chapter":18,"line_start":272,"line_end":272}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_xian_xian","name":"仙仙","alias":[],"identity":"城里最红的妓女之一","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":"healer","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"城里最红的妓女，善于逢迎","personality":{"traits":["善于逢迎","大胆直率","聪明伶俐","温柔体贴","善解人意"],"speech_style":"温柔妩媚，善于调情","temperament":"温柔妩媚"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[18],"source_refs":[{"chapter":18,"line_start":202,"line_end":202,"text":"这两个女的一个叫仙仙"}]},{"id":"char_mei_mei","name":"美美","alias":[],"identity":"城里最红的妓女之一","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":"healer","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"城里最红的妓女，善于逢迎","personality":{"traits":["善于逢迎","温柔体贴","善解人意","聪明伶俐","大方得体"],"speech_style":"温柔妩媚，善于调情","temperament":"温柔妩媚"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[18],"source_refs":[{"chapter":18,"line_start":202,"line_end":202,"text":"一个叫美美"}]},{"id":"char_qing_qing","name":"青青","alias":[],"identity":"丁鹏的妻子，狐族","faction":null,"role":"companion","archetype":"warrior","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"丁鹏的妻子，狐族天狐","personality":{"traits":["温柔贤淑","聪慧过人","深情款款","善解人意","勇敢坚强"],"speech_style":"温柔体贴，充满爱意","temperament":"温柔贤淑"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_ding_peng","type":"恋人","intensity":90,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"恩爱夫妻"}],"known_skills":["skill_tian_hu_zhi_dao"],"related_skills":["skill_tian_hu_zhi_dao"],"rag_refs":[18],"source_refs":[{"chapter":18,"line_start":262,"line_end":262,"text":"青青，你来了"}]},{"id":"char_qing_yi_shao_nv","name":"青衣少女","alias":[],"identity":"青青的丫鬟","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"青青的丫鬟，身手不凡","personality":{"traits":["机灵古怪","武功高强","忠诚不二","口齿伶俐","活泼可爱"],"speech_style":"活泼俏皮，略带调侃","temperament":"活泼开朗"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_qing_qing","type":"主仆","intensity":80,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"忠心耿耿"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[18],"source_refs":[{"chapter":18,"line_start":278,"line_end":278,"text":"只留下那个青衣的丫头在门口"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":4,"line_start":301,"line_end":400,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_qing_yi_shao_nv","speaker_name":"青衣少女","listener":null,"text":"别开玩笑，我怕痒，可受不了你胳肢……","tone":"微笑","chapter":18,"line_start":302,"line_end":302},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"","listener":null,"text":"大……大鹏鸟，我实在吃不消了，全身骨头都要散了似的……","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":312,"line_end":312},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"","listener":null,"text":"我知道，我并不认为你做得荒唐。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":328,"line_end":328},{"speaker":"char_qing_qing","speaker_name":"青青","listener":null,"text":"我没有办法，狐也有几种，我修的天狐之道。","tone":"无奈","chapter":18,"line_start":338,"line_end":338},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"","listener":null,"text":"是较为正统的那一道，练气修性，僻谷修真，而登飞仙之境。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":342,"line_end":342},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"","listener":null,"text":"我知道修得很浅，什么都还没修成，偏又孽缘难解认识了你，天狐之境是忌情欲的，我动了凡心，坏了道基，仙业无望，最多只能像个平凡的女人一样……","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":346,"line_end":346},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"","listener":null,"text":"她不是小丫头，也是狐，不过她修的是迷狐道。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":386,"line_end":386},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"","listener":null,"text":"什么？这么一点大的小鬼，居然修的这一道。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":394,"line_end":394}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_xiao_yun","name":"小云","alias":[],"identity":"青青的丫鬟，迷狐","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":"assassin","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"青青的丫鬟，修习迷狐道，擅长媚功","personality":{"traits":["羞涩内向","武功高强","忠诚不二","善于媚功","深藏不露"],"speech_style":"羞涩答答，善于调情","temperament":"羞涩内向"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_qing_qing","type":"主仆","intensity":80,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"忠心耿耿"}],"known_skills":["skill_mi_hu_zhi_dao"],"related_skills":["skill_mi_hu_zhi_dao"],"rag_refs":[18],"source_refs":[{"chapter":18,"line_start":384,"line_end":384,"text":"小云，你说的是那个小丫头？"}]}],"skills":[{"id":"skill_tian_hu_zhi_dao","name":"天狐之道","type":"内功","faction":"狐族","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"狐族正统修炼法门，练气修性，僻谷修真","techniques":[{"id":"tech_tian_hu_xiu_xing","name":"天狐修行","type":"buff","description":"练气修性，僻谷修真，而登飞仙之境"},{"id":"tech_tian_hu_zhi_lve","name":"天狐之略","type":"special","description":"鬼神莫测之机，有神妙莫测之能"}],"progression":[{"level":"初窥门径","description":"青青修得很浅，什么都还没修成"}],"effects":["增益","特殊"],"combat_style":"辅助型","rag_refs":[18],"source_refs":[{"chapter":18,"line_start":338,"line_end":338,"text":"我没有办法，狐也有几种，我修的天狐之道"}]},{"id":"skill_mi_hu_zhi_dao","name":"迷狐之道","type":"内功","faction":"狐族","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"狐族左道旁门，专修阴阳和合，采补挹注之道","techniques":[{"id":"tech_yin_yang_he_he","name":"阴阳和合","type":"buff","description":"专修阴阳和合，采补挹注之道"},{"id":"tech_mei_gong","name":"媚功","type":"debuff","description":"擅长媚功，能迷惑人心"}],"progression":[{"level":"登堂入室","description":"小云修习迷狐道，已有小成"}],"effects":["控制","增益"],"combat_style":"辅助型","rag_refs":[18],"source_refs":[{"chapter":18,"line_start":386,"line_end":386,"text":"她不是小丫头，也是狐，不过她修的是迷狐道"}]}],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":5,"line_start":401,"line_end":500,"dialogues":[{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"","listener":null,"text":"这也有道理，可是他们又如何浇灭心中的火呢？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":442,"line_end":442},{"speaker":"char_xiao_yun","speaker_name":"小云","listener":null,"text":"爷，我的年纪不小了，最少也有四五百岁了。","tone":"娇声","chapter":18,"line_start":462,"line_end":462},{"speaker":"char_xiao_yun","speaker_name":"小云","listener":null,"text":"爷不相信也没办法，不过爷见过像我这样的人没有？","tone":"微笑","chapter":18,"line_start":472,"line_end":472}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[{"id":"item_zhen","name":"针","type":"hidden_weapon","owner":"char_xiao_yun","one_line":"小云用来暗杀丁鹏的长针","description":"一根长长的，亮亮的针，虽然握着针的手在发抖，但是她仍然一咬牙，对准丁鹏的心口刺下去。","effects":["伤害"],"origin":"小云随身携带","rarity":"寻常凡品","related_characters":["char_xiao_yun","char_ding_peng"],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[18],"source_refs":[{"chapter":18,"line_start":490,"line_end":490,"text":"一根针，长长的，亮亮的针"}]}]},"entity_updates":[]}
